oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The Huntington Hayride
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Mann, Carl, 1942-; Williams, Andy; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and red on white) announcing the Huntington Hayride featuring Dixie Carter, Carl Mann, Branded Country, the Gospel Edition, Linda K., Kelly Cash, the Tennesseans, and Andy Williams at the Dixie Carter Center on November 19, December 17, and January 21. Poster features woodcuts of stars and music notes.
